          <li><strong>Five focus types</strong> — code, write, read, audio, design — each stamps a different texture into your Boulder.</li>
          <li><strong>Mountain Range gallery</strong> for retired Boulders. Release a Mountain-sized Boulder into the sea; it joins your skyline.</li>
          <li><strong>Menubar only.</strong> No Dock icon, no nagging, no streak guilt. Truly chill.</li>
        </ul>
